Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:08.97,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂 欢 节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵方法你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系统很简单 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这吗 可别搞坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 抬起手臂看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系统已经掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报支援系统在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过计算机进行的战况分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己看着办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就这样移动到环流银河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 要安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在环上开出洞来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示当前位置 固定坐标值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快重新站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求情报支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像游泳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体放松就能浮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不会游泳就先说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到机体会如此不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 宇宙中没有海嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 我们去吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是你点的少女套餐和紫菜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只要这些就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他好吃的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人还真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的事不用沮丧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经常搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德你可以再放轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松？要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大玩特玩一场就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天开始就是祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你得表现出觉得好吃的表情才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好吃的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 你还没换衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话 好男人都会被抢走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 帅哥在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算霸占人家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿一起去参观祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕鱼的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机可单独执行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉可继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这次开自己的人形机器人来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机并非人形机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是Machine Caliber-K6821
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿参加捕鱼任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员雷德少尉正在视察祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那小子不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始执行海洋生物的捕捉任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拿网去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你之前完全沉下海了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber在替我干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来稍微陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你不知道怎么花钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 这次我就特别请你搓一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当作示范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫菜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特选晚餐两人份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 特选晚餐两人份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 思乡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回到宇宙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有地图
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的生活如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和大家之间的距离 很远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃紫菜面包当然是这样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都讨厌紫菜面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙太没存在感了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没存在感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 就没什么想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回归同盟的战线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指在你现在所在的地方 在这艘船上想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己想要什么都不知道 怎么能得到别人的信赖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我合伙打捞船只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打捞船只？工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个破废铁一定能捞到大宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算赚到钱 工资也花不完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 赚到钱就去吃好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等赚到更多的钱 就去搞艘更好的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱放在手里也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要像这样去实现自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现…自己的欲望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抢着挖人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢着挖人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要合伙的话 应该找专职的我才是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你培养成一流的船只打捞师的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打捞船只的事 我不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很简单 我会教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不懂的地方只管问就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不知道怎么做 那就有样学样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别听她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合伙 好吃的要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会教你如何辨别潮汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有资质 很快就能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合伙的话 好酒随便你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子还得教你游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子的屁股随便摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 你从刚刚开始就很下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 你这贝壳屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是贝壳屁股啊 你这旱鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是旱鸭子 只是不会潜水罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 这是您的主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯 人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歼灭对象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是章鱼罢了 很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是光看到这小章鱼就吃惊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上鲸乌贼还不得吓趴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼 能吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机请求驾驶员雷德少尉支援
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part2 start
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力振荡 展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.35,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(594,650)}Gravity Waver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也好 你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在想些啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营养学上没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法应对目前情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机请求雷德少尉支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都成肉泥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 用网来捞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看别人是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要尽可能大的网
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及请求其他人形机器人的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得意个啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饱饱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电：我只能帮你到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 索敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围检测到能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险级别：低
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是光幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环流银河消失的时候便会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛子还得好好练习才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习？ 艾米 你练过舞蹈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看 艾米 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就当作刚刚的回礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 雷德哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚钱 付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起 吃好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拿到的报酬是扶持了别人的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扶持了别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人邀请我去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Chamber一起打捞船只
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为海里沉着很多东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许可以知道这颗星球以前发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去打捞船只
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能来真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你肯定会去皮尼欧那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有些东西 希望贝罗兹教我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这台人形机器人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是好像很快就会没东西可教了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 我想学到更多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 这个也中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是宝贝 要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌影 需要迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次确认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固有反应解析完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖然性99.7％。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认定对象为希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始交战 歼灭希迪亚斯
